languages.text: {n}Всячески избегая Ирлиэт, эльдары рассеиваются по поляне и пропадают в тени лесов. Эльдарка же лишь молча смотрит вслед уходящим, стиснув руки в кулак до побелевших костяшек.{/n} "Так и закончился Путь Изгоя".

{n}Avoiding Yrliet as best they can, the Aeldari scatter across the meadow and disappear into the shadows of the forest. She watches them leave, her fists clenched so hard that her knuckles have turned white.{/n} "So ended the Path of the Outcast."

languages.text: {n}艾达灵族避开伊莉耶特，三三两两地穿过草甸，消失在树林的阴影中。伊莉耶特目送着他们离开，拳头攥得连指节都发白了。{/n}“流浪者的道途也到此结束了。”

languages.text: {n}Haciendo lo posible por evitar a Yrliet, los Aeldari se dispersan por el prado y desaparecen entre las sombras del bosque. Ella los ve partir, con los puños apretados con tanta fuerza que sus nudillos están blancos.{/n} «Así termina mi Senda del Proscrito».

languages.text: {n}Les Aeldaris se dispersent dans la clairière en prenant soin d'éviter Yrliet et disparaissent dans l'obscurité de la forêt. Elle les regarde disparaître, les poings serrés si fort que ses phalanges en deviennent blanches.{/n} « Et c'est ainsi que s'achève la Voie de l'Errance. »
languages.original_text: {n}Avoiding Yrliet as best they can, the Aeldari scatter across the meadow and disappear into the shadows of the forest. She watches them leave, her fists clenched so hard that her knuckles have turned white.{/n} "So ended the Path of the Outcast."

Elle les regarde disparaître, les poings serrés si fort que ses phalanges en deviennent blanches.{/n} « Et c'est ainsi que s'achève la Voie de l'Errance. »
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: {n}Die Aeldari meiden Yrliet bestmöglich, zerstreuen sich und verschwinden in den Schatten des Waldes. Sie sieht ihnen nach und ballt die Fäuste so stark, dass ihre Knöchel sich weiß verfärben.{/n} "So endete der Pfad des Ausgestoßenen."
languages.original_text: {n}Avoiding Yrliet as best they can, the Aeldari scatter across the meadow and disappear into the shadows of the forest. She watches them leave, her fists clenched so hard that her knuckles have turned white.{/n} "So ended the Path of the Outcast."

traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: {n}アエルダリはユリエットを避けるように草原を横切り、森の影に消えていった。指の関節が真っ白になるほどに彼女は拳を強く握りしめ、彼らが去っていくのを見送った。{/n}「かくして追放者の道は終わったのだ」

traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: {n}Yrliet'i görmezden gelmeye çalışan Aeldariler, çayıra dağılıp ormanın gölgelerine doğru gözden kayboluyor. Yrliet, gidişlerini izlerken yumruklarını öyle bir sıkıyor ki elleri bembeyaz kesiliyor.{/n} "Yurtsuzun Yolu burada sona erdi."

traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion
